ass providing the common interface for all compilers. The C1 compiler (c1/c1_Compiler.hpp) provides first-tier just-in-time compilation for fast startup and initial method compilation, implementing the Compiler class derived from AbstractCompiler. The C2 compiler (opto/c2compiler.hpp) provides second-tier optimizing compilation, implementing the C2Compiler class for highly-optimized native code generation. This tiered architecture allows the JVM to balance between quick startup (C1) and peak performance (C2).\"\n}\n",
